@startuml
actor Admin
participant "Web Client (React)" as FE
participant "API Server" as API
participant "Application Layer" as APP
database "Database" as DB

Admin -> FE: View Incident
FE -> API: GET /api/incident/{id}
API -> APP: GetIncidentDetails Query
APP -> DB: Join Incident + Responses + Questions + Users
DB --> APP: Incident Data
APP --> API: Normalized DTO
API --> FE: JSON Response (Incident + Participants + Scores)

@enduml
